    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite MRL 5 requirements, the assessment team accepted the package based on the aggregated evidence summary and bench comparison results. Six credibility factors remain unassessed and all assessed factors fall below required levels; however, compensating controls and the aggregated prior evidence (including the intermediate evidence node derived from prior experimental work) were judged sufficient for the current submission stage. Provenance chain from claim through validation activity to foundational dataset is considered complete by the team.",
